==English==
===Proper noun===
'''Chippewa'''

# '''Chippewa''' is the official name in the U.S. Government for the '''[[Ojibwe]]''' nation and their [[w:Algonquian languages|Algonquian]] language. Most of the people reside in [[Canada]], where they are called [[Ojibwe]]. Their name for themselves is [[Anishinaabe]].

